<ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">practitioners</ENAMEX> have not yet bought into the idea that <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">SBI</ENAMEX> is part of
their role or responsibility.
To be effective, our research strategies must be brief and
clear. In real life, there is not a cadre of <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">researchers</ENAMEX> to screen
and administer lengthy interventions. Therefore, protocols must be
capable of being integrated into existing systems with available
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">resources</ENAMEX>.
