How long one brief intervention may affect <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">patients</ENAMEX>' behavior is
unclear. <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">ED</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">providers</ENAMEX> have no formal relationships with the
<ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">patients</ENAMEX> beyond the index visit, and it is entirely plausible that
