compelling reasons make the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">ED</ENAMEX> an important setting for alcohol
<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">interventions</ENAMEX>. First, a large number and variety of <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">patients</ENAMEX> are
